ed-full border border-(--rose-main) text-(--rose-dark)\">Inmobiliaria</span>\n        <span class=\"text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-(--rose-main) text-(--rose-dark)\">Aeronáutico</span>\n        <span class=\"text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-(--rose-main) text-(--rose-dark)\">Administrativo</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"bg-(--beige-main)\">\n    <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-360 px-6 sm:px-14 lg:px-24 py-14 sm:py-20\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-end justify-between mb-10 sm:mb-12\">\n        <h2 class=\"font-serif text-(--charcoal) text-2xl sm:text-3xl max-w-md leading-snug\">\n          Contenido escrito con el mismo <span class=\"italic text-(--rose-dark)\">rigor de nuestros casos.</span>\n        </h2>\n        <span class=\"hidden sm:block text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-(--beige-dark)\">Por qué leernos</span>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-x-10 gap-y-10 sm:gap-y-12\">\n        <div class=\"trust-item\">\n          <div class=\"h-px w-full bg-(--copper)/50 mb-4\"></div>\n          <div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-5\">\n            <span class=\"font-serif text-(--copper) text-3xl leading-none\">01</span>\n            <svg class=\"trust-icon w-6 h-6 text-(--copper) shrink-0 transition-colors\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"><path d=\"M12 3v18M4 8h16M4 8l-2 6a3 3 0 006 0zM20 8l-2 6a3 3 0 006 0z\"></path></svg>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-serif text-(--charcoal) text-xl mb-2\">Redactado por abogados en ejercicio</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-(--gray-text)\">Cada artículo pasa por el equipo especialista del área que lo desarrolla, no por redactores externos.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"trust-item\">\n          <div class=\"h-px w-full bg-(--copper)/50 mb-4\"></div>\n          <div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-5\">\n     